  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImputationStrategy  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApproxMeanSubstitution
    An imputation strategy that imputes the missing column value by approx mean of the specified column.
    MeanSubstitution
    An imputation strategy that imputes the missing column value with the mean of the specified column.
    ModeSubstitution
    An imputation strategy that imputes the column value by the mode of specified column
    NaiveBayesClassifier  
    NaiveBayesSubstitution
    An imputation strategy that is based on Naive Bayes Algorithm which is the probabilistic classifier.
    Probability  
    UnivariateLinearRegressionSubstitution
    An imputation strategy that is based on Linear Regression which is an approach for modeling the relationship between a scalar dependent variable y and an explanatory variable x.
